  <!-- About
-------------------------->

  <section id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="information col-lg-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-12">
          <h2>What is it?</h2>
          <p><span>COPAIR</span> is based on the idea of two people working together on the same computer and improving their coding skills by helping each other. We help people get together to work on their ideas!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="information col-lg-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-12">
          <%= image_tag('match.gif', class: 'match') %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row reverse">
        <div class="information col-lg-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-12">
          <h2>How does it work?</h2>
          <p>Regardless of your knowledge, you'll only need a laptop and an internet connection. Get together with your matching pair and start a project. Sharing knowledge and learning is the goal of <span>COPAIR</span>. Best of all, it's completely free!
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="information col-lg-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-12">
          <%= image_tag('laptop.gif', class: 'laptop') %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="information col-lg-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-12">
          <h2>Benefits</h2>
          <p>It might be difficult to take the first step but after you do it you will feel more confident about your skills, more prepared for future job interviews and it's a great way to network!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="information col-lg-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-12">
          <%= image_tag('benefits.gif', class: 'benefits') %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


